eles. The special concert event benefits Young Survival Coalition and will be produced by CBS Radio. The performance will celebrate the release of her highly anticipated album and will be her only U.S. concert performance this year.","month":"09","year":"2013","publishDate":"September 23, 2013","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi and Katy Perry Team in Celebration of New Album Release PRISM","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2013/citi-and-katy-perry-team-in-celebration-of-new-album-release-prism","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi today announced that it has been named the Global Industry Group Leader for Diversified Financials in the 2013/2014 Dow Jones Sustainability Index (DJSI), the first global index to track the financial performance of the leading sustainability-driven companies worldwide. This marks the 12th consecutive year Citi has been named to both the DJSI World and North America indices and the first time Citi has been named a sector leader.","month":"09","year":"2013","publishDate":"September 20, 2013","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Leads Global Diversified Financials Sector in 2013/2014 Dow Jones Sustainability Index","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2013/citi-leads-global-diversified-financials-sector-in-20132014-dow-jones-sustainability-index","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi, an official sponsor of Team USA, today announced its roster of 'Team Citi' athletes for the 2014 Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games in Sochi, Russia. Team Citi is comprised of nine Olympic and Paralympic, hopefuls and legends, representing a wide range of sports, including: alpine skiing, figure skating, ice hockey, luge, nordic combined, speed skating, Paralympic alpine skiing and sled hockey. ","month":"09","year":"2013","publishDate":"September 