ignificant savings. ","month":"07","year":"2013","publishDate":"July 16, 2013","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Expands Its Corporate Client Billing Network in Costa Rica via Strategic Partnership with Servimás","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2013/citi-expands-its-corporate-client-billing-network-in-costa-rica-via-strategic-partnership-with-servimaacutes","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup Inc. today reported net income for the second quarter 2013 of $4.2 billion, or $1.34 per diluted share, on revenues of $20.5 billion. This compared to net income of $2.9 billion, or $0.95 per diluted share, on revenues of $18.4 billion for the second quarter 2012. ","month":"07","year":"2013","publishDate":"July 15, 2013","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Reports Second Quarter 2013 Earnings per Share of $1.34; $1.25 Excluding CVA/DVA","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2013/citigroup-reports-second-quarter-2013-earnings-per-share-of-134-125-excluding-cvadva","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"<br>Earlier this morning, Citi released its earnings report for the second quarter of 2013. Chief Financial Officer John Gerspach discusses the report in this video. For more information and the full earnings report, visit the <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/global/investors\">Investor Relations section of Citigroup's website</a>.","month":"07","year":"2013","publishDate":"July 15, 2013","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Releases Second Quarter 2013 Earnings","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2013/-earlier-this-morning-citi-1"},{"summary":"Miami, Florida - Citi was named Best Cash Management House in Latin America for the fifth consecutive year and Best Flow House in Latin America in the 2