Id":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Czech Republic: Premium Forex Products Increasingly Popular with Citibank's Clients","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/cech-republic-premium-forex-products-increasingly-popular-with-citibank-s-clients","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Manila - Financial education experts and policy makers from 30 countries will gather in Manila December 5 and 6 for the ninth-annual Citi-FT Financial Education Summit, the leading international forum on financial capability. This year's event - organized by the Citi Foundation, the Pearson Foundation and the <i>Financial Times</i> and co-sponsored by IFC, Prudential and Visa - will convene more than 280 representatives from non-profit organizations, financial institutions, government agencies/regulators, multilateral institutions, microfinance institutions, educational organizations and private business.","month":"12","year":"2012","publishDate":"December 04, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Philippines Hosts International Forum on Financial Education","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/philippines-hosts-international-forum-on-financial-education","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"During the recent inaugural celebration of <a href=\"https://www.veteransweeknyc.org/\">Veterans Week in New York City</a>, the <a href=\"https://www.citifoundation.com/\">Citi Foundation</a> and <a href=\"https://www.citisalutes.com/\">Citi Salutes<strong>™</strong></a> partnered with the <a href=\"https://www.taprootfoundation.org/\">Taproot Foundation</a> on the second Citi Skills Marathon of 2012. This unique skills-based volunteering model connected the talents and professional expertise of Citi colleagues with the organizational needs of non-profit organizations that serve the military ve