reneurial training and three-year microinsurance coverage.","month":"12","year":"2012","publishDate":"December 03, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Philippines Announce 2012 Microentrepreneur of the Year Awardees","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-philippines-announce-2012-microentrepreneur-of-the-year-awardees","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"It takes optimism to launch your own business. But what if your optimism proves misplaced and the business gets into trouble? As a sole proprietor, you would be personally responsible for the liabilities of the business. That means creditors could come after your home and your personal investments.","image":"638e310da3c47c530c0a5f5d","year":"2012","publishDate":"December 03, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Starting a Business? Look to Limit Your Liability","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/starting-a-business-look-to-limit-your-liability","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"12","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"\"While the laws and cultural norms in some countries where Citi operates differ from commonly accepted global standards for human rights, Citi supports equality without regard for, among other personal characteristics, race, gender, gender identity or expression, disability, age, nationality, or sexual orientation.\"","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 30, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Statement on Online Petition Regarding Uganda","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-statement-on-online-petition-regarding-uganda","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Miami, Florid