"). The ETRUPS® are being redeemed, along with the common securities issued by Citigroup Capital XX and held by Citi, as a result of the concurrent redemption in whole by Citi of the junior subordinated debt securities held by Citigroup Capital XX which underlie the ETRUPS®. ","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 14, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Announces Redemption of Trust Preferred Securities Issued by Citigroup Capital XX","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-announces-redemption-of-trust-preferred-securities-issued-by-citigroup-capital-xx","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York - On October 17, 2012, Citigroup Inc. announced the declaration by its Board of Directors of a dividend of $0.01 per share of common stock payable on November 21, 2012, to holders of record on November 5, 2012. Effective on the payment of this dividend, an adjustment will be made to the settlement rates and certain other terms of Citi's T-DECS, as set forth below. No adjustment will be made to the terms of Citi's warrants or convertible preferred stock because the amount of the dividend to be paid is less than the threshold amount required for an adjustment. ","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 14, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Inc. Announces T-DECS Adjustments to Result From Common Dividend and Final Settlement of T-DECS on December 17, 2012","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-inc-announces-t-decs-adjustments-to-result-from-common-dividend-and-final-settlement-of-t-decs-on-december-17-2012","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"At Citi, corporate citizenship is not a stand-alone initiative. We integrate our citizenship efforts and community support into all of our core business activities.","image":"638e3125a3c47c530c0a5fc7","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 14, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Civic 50 Ranks Citi Top Bank and #2 Overall for Most Community-Minded U.S. Companies","author.jobTitle":["CEO North America"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/civic-50-ranks-citi-top-bank-and-2-overall-for-most-community-minded-us-companies","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Bill Mills"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"From November 10-12, more than 470 Citi employees, friends and family members fanned out across the greater New York region to support the massive disaster relief operation being led by the American Red Cross, which is mobilizing 7,000 volunteers to assist more than 246,000 families impacted by Hurricane Sandy. Citi volunteers answered the call to service, and performed a variety of tasks to support the relief effort.","image":"638e3126a3c47c530c0a5fd0","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 14, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi volunteers join the American Red Cross Hurricane Sandy relief effort","author.jobTitle":["Citi Community Development, Jill Kelly, Citi Community Development","Citi Community Development","Chief Operating Officer"],"url":"/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-volunteers-join-the-american-red-cross-hurricane-sandy-relief-effort","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Pat Edwards","Jill Kelly","Florencia Spangaro"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Istanbul - Citi Turkey has been named \"Best Domestic Cash Management Bank in Turkey\" in <i>Euromoney's</i> 2012 annual cash management survey. In addition, Citi also took top honors with two regional awards and 18 country awards globally.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Clients Vote Citibank Turkey as \"Best Domestic Cash Management Bank\"","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/clients-vote-citibank-turkey-as-best-domestic-cash-management-bank","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - Citigold customers now have access to Citibank's world-class priority banking products and services in the new exclusive Citigold Center branch at MOM Park Shopping Mall in Budapest. Located in one of the city's most high profile shopping malls, the Citigold Center uses innovative elements of modern design and technology to enhance the customers' banking experience.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Hungary Opens an Exclusive Citigold Center with Digital Features at MOM Park Shopping Mall in Budapest","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-hungary-opens-an-exclusive-citigold-center-with-digital-features-at-mom-park-shopping-mall-in-budapest","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi ThankYou® Rewards members now have another place where they can use their ThankYou Points: Amazon.com. Beginning this holiday shopping season, eligible Citi ThankYou members can use their points to purchase millions of products at Amazon.com. ThankYou members with a Citi credit card enrolled in Citi ThankYou Rewards are currently eligible to use their points at Amazon.com.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi ThankYou® Rewards Members Can Now Shop with Points at Amazon.com","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-thankyou-rewards-members-can-now-shop-with-points-at-amaoncom","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - This holiday season, shoppers hunting for a lower price can rest easier when they make purchases on their eligible Citi credit card and use Citi Price Rewind, a unique price protection program. After a Citi cardmember purchases and registers an eligible item, Price Rewind will search hundreds of retailers' sites for 30 days after the purchase to find a lower price. If a price is at least $25 less than what the cardmember paid, Citi will refund the difference in price - up to $250 per item. Citi Price Rewind is a complimentary benefit available year-round on eligible Citi consumer credit cards.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi® Price Rewind Enables Citi Credit Cardmembers to Save on Purchases After Checkout","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-price-rewind-enables-citi-credit-cardmembers-to-save-on-purchases-after-checkout","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Through our <a href=\"https://www.citisalutes.com/\">Citi Salutes™</a> initiative, Citi is proud to support the men and women who have served our country, on Veterans Day and every day.","image":"638e312aa3c47c530c0a5fe3","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Supporting Those Who Serve: On Veterans Day and Every Day","author.jobTitle":["Regional Head of Markets, North America, Citi","Citi Pride Affinity Co-lead"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/supporting-those-who-serve-on-veterans-day-and-every-day","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Suni Harford","Bob Annibale"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"The third in our series highlighting the finalists for the FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards, this post examines four healthcare candidates whose work continues to make healthy living and medical services a priority in cities worldwide. Be sure to visit <a href=\"https://facebook.com/citi\">Citi's Facebook page</a> to tell us which finalists you think are the most ingenious, and check back later this month for profiles on finalists in the final category, education.","image":"638e312ea3c47c530c0a5fee","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards - Meet the Healthcare Finalists","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/ftciti-ingenuity-awards---meet-the-healthcare-finalists","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Looking to provide financial help to family members? Here are three ways you can pass along money without worrying about the federal gift tax.","image":"638e312fa3c47c530c0a5ff5","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 13, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Three Ways to Give--Without Worrying About Gift Taxes","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/three-ways-to-give--without-worrying-about-gift-taxes","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"<strong>A rebound in economic data is likely but it may be more of a 2013 development. </strong>The credit conditions recovery, which began in late 4Q11, already is beginning to have impact on different reports such as job trends and the ISM. But it seems more probable that the improvements will accelerate in early 2013, leaving the proponents of a seasonal fourth quarter market surge somewhat disappointed.","image":"638e3130a3c47c530c0a5ffc","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 12, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Equity Strategy: November 2012 Chart of the Month","author.jobTitle":["Chief US Equity Strategist, Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/equity-strategy-november-chart-of-the-month","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Tobias Levkovich"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"New York - Today, Citi announced $500,000 in emergency funding to five community organizations to expand their relief efforts in neighborhoods across New York City, Long Island and New Jersey that are struggling in the aftermath of Hurricane Sandy. This latest funding is part of Citi's support of relief and recovery efforts in the region's hardest hit communities.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Announces $500,000 to Support Community-Based Organizations on the Frontline of Hurricane Sandy Relief Efforts","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-announces-500000-to-support-community-based-organiations-on-the-frontline-of-hurricane-sandy-relief-efforts","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Because of the large geographic impact of Hurricane Sandy, many communities have been affected in very different ways and are now confronting a range of challenges based on the storm's impact. Frontline community-based organizations are critical to the social and economic health of many of these severely affected neighborhoods.","month":"11","author.displayName":["Bob Annibale"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"November 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Supporting Community-Based Organizations on the Frontline of Hurricane Sandy Relief Efforts","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Citi Pride Affinity Co-lead"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/supporting-community-based-organizations-on-the-frontline-of-hurricane-sandy-relief-efforts","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 32nd installment below covers how the bank merged with Banamex. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/10/citi-turns-200-courage-in-a-crisis.shtml\">Read the 31st installment explaining how Citi employees came together during the tragic events on September 11th, 2001, here</a>.","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Mergers create banking giants abroad","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-mergers-create-banking-giants-abroad","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi has been recognized as the top financial services company and the second-ranked overall organization in The Civic 50 survey - the first comprehensive ranking of S&P 500 corporations that best use their time, talent and resources to improve the quality of life in the communities where they do business. The survey was conducted by the National Conference on Citizenship (NCoC) and Points of Light, the nation's definitive experts on civic engagement, in partnership with Bloomberg LP.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 08, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Named #1 Financial Services Company and #2 Overall in Ranking of Top 50 Community-Minded U.S. Companies","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-named-1-financial-services-company-and-2-overall-in-ranking-of-top-50-community-minded-us-companies","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Citibank Taiwan celebrated the relocation of its Chiayi Branch in southern Taiwan today with an opening ceremony attended by Victor Kuan, Citibank Taiwan Chairman; Yunny Lee, Citibank Taiwan Head of Retail Banking; Lin Chien-chih, Senior Advisor to President Ma Ying-jeou; and Huang Min-hui, Mayor of Chiayi City.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 08, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Taiwan Celebrates Relocation of Chiayi Branch with Launch of Institutional & High Net Worth Fund Platform","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-taiwan-celebrates-relocation-of-chiayi-branch-with-launch-of-institutional-high-net-worth-fund-platform","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/citi/about/leaders/michael-corbat-ceo-bio.html\">Citi CEO Michael Corbat</a> said earlier this week \"Our Hurricane Sandy relief programs are intended to alleviate some of the financial hardships facing our customers so they can focus on the most pressing issues in front of them. Citi is committed to helping our customers recover and rebuild by being sensitive and accommodating to their needs.\"","month":"11","author.displayName":["Sanjiv Das"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"November 08, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Broadens Relief for Mortgage Customers Following Hurricane Sandy","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["CEO, CitiMortgage"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-broadens-relief-for-mortgage-customers-following-hurricane-sandy","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Bucharest, Romania - Citibank Romania customers can now benefit from Aegon Prestige, a new financial product developed by Aegon, which combines the characteristics of life insurance products with the open architecture of investment funds.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 07, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Romania: Aegon Prestige - The New Insurance and Capital Growth Tool for Citibank Clients","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/romania-aegon-prestige-the-new-insurance-and-capital-growth-tool-for-citibank-clients","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Moscow - Citi Russia hosted a briefing on \"The Social Impacts of Microfinancing: Myths or Reality?\" Mikhail Mamuta, President of the Russian Microfinance Center (RMC), presented the results of a study on the influence of microfinance on the lives of low-income clients. The study assessed indicators in a variety of areas related to both business and family. ","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 06, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Russia: Microfinance Improves the Financial Well-Being of Russians","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-russia-microfinance-improves-the-financial-well-being-of-russians","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"A new documentary film \"<a href=\"https://afootinthedoor.info/\">A Foot in the Door</a>\" tells the story of the nation's first universal college savings program, San Francisco's <a href=\"https://www.k2csf.org/\">Kindergarten to College</a>, through the personal experiences of participating students and parents.","month":"11","author.displayName":["Jenny Flores"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"November 06, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Kindergarten to College: A Foot in the Door","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Northern California Regional Director, Citi Community Development"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/kindergarten-to-college-a-foot-in-the-door","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"<p class=\"blog-listing-body\">Hurricane Sandy exacted an enormous toll on the Mid-Atlantic and Northeast, decimating neighborhoods, destroying livelihoods, and, most tragically, taking lives. Since our founding 200 years ago, Citi has been proud to support the communities we serve, especially our hometown of New York City and during the past week, we reinforced this commitment by joining our neighbors in extending assistance to those in need.</p>,<p class=\"blog-listing-body\">In the immediate aftermath of the storm, the Citi Foundation donated $1 million to the American Red Cross to support post-Sandy relief and recovery efforts. The $1 million donation supplements a $500,000 grant that the Citi Foundation provides to the Red Cross every year to support the organization's relief activities. Citi has also contributed to organizations focused on local relief and recovery efforts, including the Staten Island-based Stephen Siller Tunnel to Towers Foundation. We also enabled Citi ThankYou® Rewards members to use their points to make donations to the Red Cross at <a href=\"https://www.thankyou.com/\">www.thankyou.com</a>. <br></p>","image":"638e3136a3c47c530c0a6017","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 06, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Following Hurricane Sandy, Citi is trying to help by doing its Part","author.jobTitle":["CEO, Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/following-hurricane-sandy-citi-is-trying-to-help-by-doing-its-part","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Mike Corbat"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Citi was ranked as Top Rated in Asia Pacific by respondents in both the 2012 Private Equity Fund Administration survey and the 2012 Hedge Fund Administration survey conducted by <i>Global Custodian</i>.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 05, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Earns Top Ratings for Private Equity and Hedge Fund Administration in Asia Pacific","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-earns-top-ratings-for-private-equity-and-hedge-fund-administration-in-asia-pacific","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"It's been a good year for stocks, which means you might want to think about \"rebalancing.\" What's that? Imagine your goal is a portfolio with 60% in U.S. and foreign stocks and 40% in high-quality bonds, certificates of deposit and other conservative investments, and that was the mix you owned at the start of 2012. Even if you haven't done any trading this year, you may now have significantly more than 60% in shares, thanks to the stock market's rise.","image":"638e3138a3c47c530c0a6020","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 05, 2012","type":"insights","title":"You May Be Unbalanced, Thanks to Rising Share Prices","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/you-may-be-unbalanced-thanks-to-rising-share-prices","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"11","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"New York - Following the destruction across the eastern part of the United States caused by Hurricane Sandy, Citi announced today that in addition to the already expanded services for impacted area customers, it is further broadening its service relief for mortgage customers, including suspending foreclosure sales in declared disaster areas.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 04, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"U.S.: Citi Broadens Relief for Mortgage Customers Following Hurricane Sandy","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/us-citi-broadens-relief-for-mortgage-customers-following-hurricane-sandy","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Citibank (China) Co. Ltd. (\"Citi\") and the China Banking Association announced the winners of the eighth annual Microentrepreneurship Awards in China. The awards ceremony to commend the outstanding microentrepreneurs and institutions in the microfinance field in the past year was held in Haikou with more than 150 microfinance practitioners in attendance.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 03, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"2012 China Banking Association - Citi Microentrepreneurship Awards Announced in Haikou","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/2012-china-banking-association--citi-microentrepreneurship-awards-announced-in-haikou","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Bangkok - Citi congratulated THAI on the continued expansion of their fleet of Airbus A380s. Building upon their strong partnership spanning over a decade, Citi Country Officer and Country Head Darren Buckley said: \"Citi is delighted to play a role in this monumental occasion for THAI. The Airbus A380 heralds a new era of efficient and technologically advanced aircraft, enabling THAI to provide world-class service to its customers on key Asian and Intercontinental routes. Over Citi's 200 year history, we have stood for progress, backing such initiatives as uniform cargo containers, the development of the commercial airliner, pioneering the ATM and launching Thailand's first broadband satellite. Citi's partnership with THAI's A380 expansion marks yet another proud milestone in that history.\"","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 02, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"THAI and Citi Celebrate the Expansion of THAI's A380 fleet","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/thai-and-citi-celebrate-the-expansion-of-thai-s-a380-fleet","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Following our recent post examining the energy category finalists for the FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards, this post explores the top candidates for infrastructure whose innovation is helping to fuel growth and economic progress in urban centers worldwide. Be sure to visit <a href=\"https://facebook.com/citi\">Citi's Facebook page</a> to tell us which of the below finalists you think is most ingenious.","image":"638e3139a3c47c530c0a6027","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 02, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards - Meet the Infrastructure Finalists","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/ftciti-ingenuity-awards---meet-the-infrastructure-finalists","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Hong Kong/Singapore - Citi has won the \"Client Clearing Provider of the Year\" award from <i>Asia Risk</i> magazine, a financial risk management publication focused on economic and regulatory risk capital in Asia Pacific.","month":"11","year":"2012","publishDate":"November 01, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Named Client Clearing Provider of the Year","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-named-client-clearing-provider-of-the-year","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Miami, Florida - Citi has been named <i>\"Best Regional Derivatives Provider in Latin America\"</i> by <i>Global Finance</i> magazine, for the second consecutive year, as part of the eighth annual \"World's Best Derivatives Providers\" awards for 2012. A full report on the awards will be published in the December issue of the prestigious publication.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 31, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Named \"Best Regional Derivatives Provider\" in Latin America by Global Finance Magazine for Second Consecutive Year","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-named-best-regional-derivatives-provider-in-latin-america-by-global-finance-magaine-for-second-consecutive-year","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"New York - The Citi Foundation today announced it has donated $1 million to the American Red Cross to help the organization with relief and recovery efforts in the aftermath of Hurricane Sandy. The $1 million contribution is in addition to the Citi Foundation's annual $500,000 grant to the Red Cross to support its Annual Disaster Giving Program. Citi is also providing financial recovery solutions for customers affected by the storm including providing access to cash and waiving select fees.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 31, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi and the Citi Foundation Donate $1 Million to American Red Cross","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-and-the-citi-foundation-donate-1-million-to-american-red-cross","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"The Citi Foundation provides the American Red Cross with an annual $500,000 grant for its disaster relief efforts in the U.S. In response to the damage caused by Hurricane Sandy, the Citi Foundation is committing an additional $1 million to their relief and recovery efforts.","image":"638e313ba3c47c530c0a602e","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 31, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"The Citi Foundation Commits An Additional $1M to Red Cross for Hurricane Sandy Relief and Recovery Efforts","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/-the-citi-foundation","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - Customers calling CitiPhone from a domestic mobile phone number registered in advance with Citibank will now hear a personalized menu, tailored to the products and selected information most relevant to them. Customers will no longer need to input their 16-digit debit or credit card number or the loan agreement ID number. They simply enter their four-digit telephone PIN code, and the system will immediately recognize and identify them and instantly offer a personalized menu.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 29, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Hungary Offers New Mobile Phone Recognition Feature on CitiPhone","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-hungary-offers-new-mobile-phone-recognition-feature-on-citiphone","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"<strong>Meet the Finalists: Energy </strong>","image":"638e313ca3c47c530c0a6035","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 29, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards: Meet the Finalists","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/ftciti-ingenuity-awards-meet-the-finalists","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"With interest rates at historic lows, many folks are looking to purchase homes, refinance existing mortgages and buy new cars. But whatever your reason for borrowing, you should probably first check your credit history and credit score.","image":"638e313ea3c47c530c0a603c","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 29, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Want to Take Advantage of Low Rates? Know Your Credit Score","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/want-to-take-advantage-of-low-rates-know-your-credit-score","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Wuhan - The winners of the eighth annual \"Citi Cup\" Financial IT Application Competition were announced today at Wuhan University. A team from Wuhan University won the highly-coveted Citi Cup from a field of 123 teams for its project on the smart-loan system for micro-finance institutions. ","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 27, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"China: Winners of \"Citi Cup\" Financial IT Application Competition Announced in Wuhan","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/china-winners-of-citi-cup-financial-it-application-competition-announced-in-wuhan","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 31st installation below covers how Citi employees came together during the tragic events on September 11th, 2001. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/10/citi-turns-200-connecting-the-dots.shtml\">Read the 30th installment explaining how the bank enhanced its foreign operations for international customers, here</a>.","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 26, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Courage in a crisis","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-courage-in-a-crisis","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - Citi Hungary and the Corvinus University launched the 2012-2013 Corvinus University-Citibank Education Program on October 18 at the Corvinus Campus in Budapest. Students from Corvinus University's Enterprise Finances Department will participate in the program, which aims to enhance students' career prospects through interaction with Citi volunteers and participation in seminars. ","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 25, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Hungary Launches 2012-2013 Corvinus University-Citibank Education Program","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-hungary-launches-2012-2013-corvinus-university-citibank-education-program","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Head of Innovation Lab Keng-Mun Lee (left) receiving the award from Singapore's Minister for Information, Communications and the Arts Dr. Yaacob Ibrahimp","image":"638e3141a3c47c530c0a6047","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 25, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi Innovation Lab Receives High Honor for Use of Infocomm Technology","author.jobTitle":["Citi Innovation Lab Head, Singapore"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-innovation-lab-receives-high-honor-for-use-of-infocomm-technology","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["Keng-Mun Lee"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup today announced that it has been ranked the greenest bank in the United States by <em>Newsweek</em> magazine. The annual <a href=\"http://www.Newsweek.com/green\" target=\"blank\"><em>Newsweek</em> Green Rankings®</a> comprehensively assess the environmental performance of the largest publicly traded companies in the U.S. and around the world. Citi was ranked the 17th greenest company in the United States, the highest ranking of any U.S.-based bank for the second year in a row.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 24, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Ranked Greenest U.S. Bank by Newsweek Magazine","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-ranked-greenest-us-bank-by-newsweek-magaine","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"One question we hear a lot is, \"How do you prepare to launch a startup?\"","image":"638e30fda3c47c530c0a5f13","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 24, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Meet Gagan Biyani of Udemy on #StartupLab","author.jobTitle":["The Young Entrepreneur Council"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/meet-gagan-biyani-of-udemy-on-startuplab","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["The Young Entrepreneur Council"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Singapore - Citi Transaction Services (CTS) is proud to announce it has been awarded the prestigious National Infocomm Award (NIA). Citi Innovation Lab won the category for \"Most Innovative Use of Infocomm Technology, Private Sector (General)\" for its Citi Interactive Solutions software. The award, jointly organized by the Infocomm Development Authority of Singapore (IDA) and the Singapore infocomm Technology Federation (SiTF), is Singapore's highest accolade for infocomm innovation.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Innovation Lab Wins Prestigious National Infocomm Award 2012","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-innovation-lab-wins-prestigious-national-infocomm-award-2012","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Citibank Taiwan has been named the '2012 Most Admired Company in Banking' by <i>CommonWealth Magazine</i>. This is Citi's 18th consecutive win since the award was launched in 1994.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Taiwan Wins Most Admired Company Award for 18th Consecutive Year","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-taiwan-wins-most-admired-company-award-for-18th-consecutive-year","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Kuala Lumpur - Citi and ERA Consumer today kicked off \"My First Ringgit,\" a customized financial education program aimed at educating and instilling good financial habits among young children. A component of Citi's \"Stretching Your Ringgit\" financial education series, \"My First Ringgit\" aims to reach 800 kindergarten children between the ages of four and six in both urban and rural areas in Malaysia.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 22, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Malaysia: Citi and ERA Consumer Spearhead Money Management Program for Pre-school Children","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/malaysia-citi-and-era-consumer-spearhead-money-management-program-for-pre-school-children","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"We spend decades preparing financially for retirement, but we often give little thought to what we'll do with all that free time. Yet it's important to have a sense of purpose to our lives, even after we quit the workforce. Indeed, to have a fulfilling retirement, we'll likely want to engage in activities that we think are important, we find challenging and we're passionate about. But how can we figure out what a fulfilling retirement looks like? Try these five steps:","image":"638e3146a3c47c530c0a6057","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 22, 2012","type":"insights","title":"You Have Enough Money to Retire. Now What?","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/you-have-enough-money-to-retire-now-what","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 30th installation below covers how the bank's flourishing business helped provide processing and clearing for international customers. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/10/citi-turns-200-bank-deals-with-financial-panics.shtml\">Read the 29th installment explaining how the bank dealt with financial panics in the early 1990s, here</a>.","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 19, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Connecting the dots","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-connecting-the-dots","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"The Citibank Royal Orchid Plus cobranded credit card, introduced more than a decade ago, pioneered travel rewards that catered to frequent travelers. The card has stimulated growth in both the credit card and travel industries.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi and Thai Airways Introduce \"Citibank Royal Orchid Plus Preferred\" Card with Enhanced Privileges and Fastest Mile-Accumulation","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-and-thai-airways-introduce-citibank-royal-orchid-plus-preferred-card-with-enhanced-privileges-and-fastest-mile-accumulation","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - The Board of Directors of Citigroup Inc. today declared a quarterly dividend on the company's common stock of $0.01 per share, payable on November 21, 2012, to stockholders of record on November 5, 2012.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Declares Dividends","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-declares-dividends-11","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York - Today, <a href=\"http://www.policymap.com/\" target=\"blank\">PolicyMap</a> and <a href=\"http://citicommunitydevelopment.com/citi/citizen/community/\">Citi Community Development</a> launched <a href=\"http://www.mydistrictdata.com/\" target=\"blank\">My District Data</a>, an interactive, web-based tool that offers a simple yet powerful way to examine the state of every Congressional district in the country through a series of on-demand reports based on economic, employment, financial, educational and housing conditions. Developed for legislators and their advisers, as well as community organizations and local residents, the free tool aggregates a range of granular data -- for the first time broken down to match the irregular borders of Congressional districts -- to present a district snapshot intended to inform smart policy-making.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"PolicyMap and Citi Community Development Launch My District Data, Offering Dynamic Data Analysis of Every U.S. Congressional District","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/policymap-and-citi-community-development-launch-my-district-data-offering-dynamic-data-analysis-of-every-us-congressional-district","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - NESsT and Citibank Hungary today announced the launch of the 2012/2013 NESsT-Citibank Social Enterprise Development Program in the business sector, the fourth of its kind in Hungary. Fifteen enterprises will be selected to participate in this comprehensive management training and financing program. Applications from businesses which in addition to generating a profit, also aim to solve critical social problems will be considered. Operating in the private sector, they also seek to improve local communities through increased employment opportunities, access to health and education services, reduced energy and resource consumption, or other environmental programs.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Hungary and NESsT Launch 2012 Social Enterprise Development Program","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-hungary-and-nesst-launch-2012-social-enterprise-development-program","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Public policy decisions that impact the communities we serve are not always made with the benefit of accurate, targeted data. The irregular borders of Congressional districts force policy practitioners to cull data from a range of sources across overlapping geographies to produce an inherently incomplete picture of economic, employment, financial, educational and housing conditions at the district level.","image":"638e3148a3c47c530c0a6062","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 17, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Smart Policy-Making Requires Dynamic Data Analysis","author.jobTitle":["Citi Pride Affinity Co-lead","President, PolicyMap"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/smart-policy-making-requires-dynamic-data-analysis","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["Bob Annibale","Maggie McCullough"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jharthorne\">John Harthorne</a>, Founder and CEO of <a href=\"https://masschallenge.org/\">MassChallenge</a> (a Boston startup accelerator and competition), is kind of one of our heroes.","image":"638e30fda3c47c530c0a5f13","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 17, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Meet John Harthorne of MassChallenge on #StartupLab","author.jobTitle":["The Young Entrepreneur Council"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/meet-john-harthorne-of-masschallenge-on-startuplab","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"10","author.displayName":["The Young Entrepreneur Council"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"London - Building on the recent successful launch of its Renminbi (RMB) cash management and trade solution in the U.K., Citi has shown a significant growth of RMB transactions generated out of London and has expanded its offshore RMB offering into Nigeria, South Africa, Kenya, Cameroon and Zambia.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Reports Significant Uptake of Renminbi Offshore Services in EMEA and Expands Renminbi Capabilities Across Africa","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-reports-significant-uptake-of-renminbi-offshore-services-in-emea-and-expands-renminbi-capabilities-across-africa","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - Citibank Hungary is first in the Hungarian market to offer its credit card customers a MasterCard PayPass-enabled Sticker that allows them to make payments at PayPass terminals in a fast and convenient way for purchases up to HUF 5,000. The Sticker can be placed on the back of mobile phones or any other personal objects, such as business card holders, purses or notebooks, and it is available for customers holding a Citi Life Multipartner Reward Credit Card, a Shell-Citibank or a Telekom-Citibank co-branded card.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi First to Offer Contactless PayPass Stickers in Hungary","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-first-to-offer-contactless-paypass-stickers-in-hungary","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi Community Development was nationally recognized for its support of the Platform to Employment program during the American Bankers Association's Annual Convention in San Diego. Citi received the first-ever <a href=\"http://www.aba.com/About/Pages/CommunityCommitmentAwards.aspx\" target=\"blank\">Community Commitment Award</a> in the Economic Development category for its collaboration with The WorkPlace to address the needs of the long-term unemployed.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Community Development Receives Inaugural Community Commitment Award from the American Bankers Association","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-community-development-receives-inaugural-community-commitment-award-from-the-american-bankers-association","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"New York - Michael E. O'Neill, Chairman of the Citigroup Board of Directors, and <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/citi/about/leaders/michael-corbat-ceo-bio.html\">Michael Corbat</a>, Chief Executive Officer, will host a teleconference on Tuesday, October 16, 2012 at 4:30 p.m. (Eastern).","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Chairman Michael E. O'Neill and CEO Michael Corbat to Host Analyst Conference Call","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-chairman-michael-e-o-neill-and-ceo-michael-corbat-to-host-analyst-conference-call","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York - The Board of Directors of Citigroup today announced that Vikram Pandit has stepped down as the Company's Chief Executive Officer and as a member of the Board, effective immediately. The Board also announced it has unanimously elected <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/citi/about/leaders/michael-corbat-ceo-bio.html\">Michael Corbat</a> CEO and a director of the Board. Mr. Corbat previously served as Citigroup's CEO of Europe, Middle East and Africa.","month":"10","year":"2012","publishDate":"October 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Vikram Pandit Steps Down as CEO of Citigroup; Board of Directors Elects Michael Corbat as CEO","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/vikram-pandit-steps-down-as-ceo-of-citigroup-board-of-directors-elects-michael-corbat-as-ceo","tags":["