ut the re-making of Citigroup after the global financial crisis. In this interview, CEO Pandit discusses how Citi's leadership team have refocused the institution on its core strengths and have made it a smaller, simpler, safer, and stronger organization. CEO Pandit also explains how Citi has embarked on a cultural transformation based on the concept of \"Responsible Finance,\" Citi's support for regulatory changes taking place, and Citi's roadmap of focusing on emerging markets, urbanization, and digitization.","image":"638e3179a3c47c530c0a6145","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Architect of the New Citi: The Business Times Interviews Citi CEO Pandit","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/architect-of-the-new-citi-the-business-times-interviews-citi-ceo-pandit","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"To celebrate Citi's 200th anniversary, we wanted to do something special. So, for the first time in Citi's history, we sponsored the 2012 U.S. Olympic and Paralympic Team. The sponsorship exceeded our expectations in every way.","image":"638e317ba3c47c530c0a614f","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 17, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi Celebrates $500,000 Donation to Benefit Sport Programs Across U.S.","author.jobTitle":["Executive Vice President | Enterprise Services and Public Affairs"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-celebrates-500000-donation-to-benefit-sport-programs-across-us","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"09","author.displayName":["Ed Skyler"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"It isn't what you make. It's what you keep.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"September 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Double Trouble: Watch Out for Taxes and Inflation","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/double-trouble-watch-out-for-taxes-and-inflation","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Washington, D.C. - Today, the FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards Healthcare Forum convened industry leaders, policy experts, academics and practitioners to discuss the challenges and opportunities in the U.S. healthcare sector and explore ways to accelerate innovative strategies in urban areas.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 14, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Healthcare Leaders Call for Investment in IT and Incentivizing Innovation to Address Urban Health Needs","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/healthcare-leaders-call-for-investment-in-it-and-incentiviing-innovation-to-address-urban-health-needs","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Asunción, Paraguay - On Sept. 22, <a href=\"http://www.citi.com.py/\" target=\"blank\">Citi Paraguay</a> marks 54 years of uninterrupted operations here. The institution opened its doors in this country in 1958 and has more than five decades of successful operations and experience behind it in Paraguay.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 14, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Paraguay Celebrates Its 54th Anniversary","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-paraguay-celebrates-its-54th-anniversary","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 26th installation below covers how the credit card business revolutionized banking. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/09/citi-turns-200-focus-shifts-to-retail-banking.shtml\">Read the 25th installment explaining how business focus shifted to retail banking and how the ATM impacted the consumer experience, here</a>.","image":"638e3180a3c47c530c0a6162","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 14, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Cards revolutionize banking","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-cards-revolutionize-banking","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/rcs/citigpa/storage/public/CitiFieldAngie.jpg\"></a>We recently had the privilege of standing under the bright lights of Citi Field alongside three amazing people: a Major League Baseball Hall of Famer, a Team Citi Paralympian and an inspiring community volunteer. What Tom Seaver, Carlos Leon and Mary Gallagher have in common - which we also share - is a tremendous sense of pride for being part of a community of people who have served our country. As co-chairs of the Citi Military Veterans Network - NYC, it was an honor to participate in such a meaningful tribute to military service.","image":"638e3181a3c47c530c0a6169","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 14, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Honoring Veterans, Military Families and Survivors at Citi Field","author.jobTitle":["Vice President, Prime Finance","Associate, Citi Transaction Services"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/honoring-veterans-military-families-and-survivors-at-citi-field","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"09","author.displayName":["Sam LaNasa","Ron Lobato"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Warsaw, Poland - Since April 2012, Citi Handlowy's corporate clients have been able to use CitiDirect Mobile, a mobile banking solution designed for large companies. In the second half of the year, the bank launched CitiDirect EB - a single-login financial services system. It is a comprehensive electronic banking solution takes makes it possible to use a single token-generated password to gain access both to the corporate account and to the CitiTrade Portal, a dedicated trade-financing module. This allows our corporate clients to take advantage of state-of-the-art technology to manage their funds with ease.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Poland: CitiDirect EB — An Innovative Solution for Businesses","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/poland-citidirect-eb-an-innovative-solution-for-businesses","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - In line with Citi's commitment to support local communities and promote diversity internally and externally around the globe, Citi Hungary's Community Volunteering Committee has organized a Roma Art Exhibition at its headquarters in Budapest. Talented, young artists who are members of the Budapest Roma Gallery Association will have their paintings showcased on walls of the corridors and offices of the Citi Service Center from September 12 to October 8, 2012.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Hungary Celebrates Diversity with a Roma Art Exhibition","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-hungary-celebrates-diversity-with-a-roma-art-exhibition","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"New York and Fort Worth, Texas - Exclusively for Citi® / AAdvantage® cardmembers, Citi and American Airlines today announced the Citi® / AAdvantage® Card Love the Journey Concert Series. The events, which take place in New York and Los Angeles this October, will feature performances by Alicia Keys and Maroon 5, who will share their music and stories of their journeys to stardom.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi and American Airlines Announce Exclusive Concerts Featuring Alicia Keys and Maroon 5","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-and-american-airlines-announce-exclusive-concerts-featuring-alicia-keys-and-maroon-5","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"<p><strong>The Panic/Euphoria Model has moved back into complacency. </strong>The closely watched sentiment gauge is beginning to warn of an investment community that appears to have become complacent again, as was the case in late March/early April 2012 and in April/May 2011 right in front of equity market wobbles. With September historically being a challenging month for stocks, such signals should be carefully monitored.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","image":"638e318ca3c47c530c0a6192","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 13, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Equity Strategy: September 2012 Chart of the Month","author.jobTitle":["Chief US Equity Strategist, Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/equity-strategy-september-2012-chart-of-the-month","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"09","author.displayName":["Tobias Levkovich"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Prague - Citibank Europe plc launched a new service in September 2012 that will allow Citi credit card holders to make the Centralized Household Payment Collection (CHPC) payments and payments for the services provided by Telefónica Czech Republic, a.s. by direct debit from Citi credit cards. Establishing the service and payments is entirely free of charge and, in addition, clients can use all benefits that Citi credit cards offer. Citibank is the first bank in the Czech market to offer this service to clients.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank is the First Bank in the Czech Market to Offer CHPC Payments and O2 Service Payments by Direct Debit from Credit Cards","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-is-the-first-bank-in-the-cech-market-to-offer-chpc-payments-and-o2-service-payments-by-direct-debit-from-credit-cards","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Port of Spain, Trinidad & Tobago - Citi recently announced the appointment of Dennis Evans as Cluster Head for the Caribbean in addition to his current responsibility of Citi Country Officer (CCO) for the Trinidad Hub. In this capacity, all Caribbean CCOs in the Bahamas, Dominican Republic, Haiti, Jamaica and Puerto Rico will report to Dennis. Additionally, Product and Function Heads covering the Caribbean will matrix report to Dennis as well, ensuring total accountability and alignment of our strategy and priorities for the Cluster.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Latin America Announces Dennis Evans as Cluster Head for the Caribbean","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-latin-america-announces-dennis-evans-as-cluster-head-for-the-caribbean","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"Citi® Global Consumer Chief Marketing and Internet Officer Michelle Peluso today was appointed to the new Consumer Advisory Board of the Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB). CFPB Director Rich Cordray announced the composition of the 25-member board today after a seven-month selection process. The CFPB created the Board of consumer experts from outside the federal government to provide advice to CFPB leadership on a broad range of consumer financial issues and emerging market trends.","month":"09","year":"2012","publishDate":"September 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Global Consumer Bank Executive Michelle Peluso Appointed to CFPB's Consumer Advisory Board"