release/2012/cech-republic-citi-premium-offers-superior-assessment-of-financial-means-wide-range-of-payment-tools-abundant-investment-opportunities","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/05/citis-thought-leadership-product-suite-citi-gps-global-perspectives-solutions-now-online.shtml\">Citi Global Perspectives & Solutions (Citi GPS) is Citi's latest thought leadership initiative</a> through which we are delivering insights and viewpoints on compelling issues and structural thematic trends in the global economy. In the most recent Citi GPS report: \"CHINA & EMERGING MARKETS: China is about to rebalance. How will EM be affected?\", Citi Chief Emerging Market Economist, David Lubin, delves into China's investment-driven growth model and the decisive impact it has had on emerging economies in the past 10 years.","image":"638e3159a3c47c530c0a60b6","month":"08","year":"2012","publishDate":"August 02, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"China & Emerging Markets: China is about to rebalance. How will EM be affected?","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/china-emerging-markets-china-is-about-to-rebalance-how-will-em-be-affected","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"New York - <a href=\"http://www.womenandco.com/\" target=\"blank\">Women & Co.</a>, Citi's personal finance resource for women, and <a href=\"http://www.parenting.com/\" target=\"blank\">Parenting.com</a>, online home of <i>Parenting</i> and <i>Babytalk</i> magazines, today released results from their 2012 Back-to-School Spending Report, providing an in-depth look at how moms really feel about shopping and school-related costs this year. According to a survey of 1,000 moms, 60 percent say that clothing will be their biggest expense this year - with 91 percent admitting to spending more on their kids' wardrobes than their own. On average, families are planning on spending $131 on clothing and $48 on school supplies - per child.","month":"08","year":"2012","publishDate":"August 01, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"U.S.: Women & Co./Parenting.com Survey: Nine Out of 10 Moms Spend More on Kids' Fall Wardrobes than Their Own","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/us-women-coparentingcom-survey-nine-out-of-10-moms-spend-more-on-kids-fall-wardrobes-than-their-own","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/rcs/citigpa/storage/public/citiopen.jpg\"></a>Washingtonians have long marked the peak of summer with an annual tennis tournament, drawing high profile players to compete under the sweltering DC sun. We are again in the midst of the Citi Open, which began July 28 and will run through August 4, at the William H.G. FitzGerald Tennis Center in Rock Creek Park. With Citi taking over as the tournament's title sponsor, we have seen the event grow both on and off the court this year.","image":"638e31aea3c47c530c0a6239","year":"2012","publishDate":"August 01, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi Open Tennis Tournament - Helping At-Risk Youth Both On and Off the Court","author.jobTitle":["Former United States Senator and Vice President of Facilities, Washington Tennis and Education Foundation"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-open-tennis-tournament---helping-at-risk-youth-both-on-and-off-the-court","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"08","author.displayName":["John Breaux"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Warsaw - Citi Handlowy has been included in the RESPECT Index for the fifth consecutive time and has appeared in each edition since it was launched by the Warsaw Stock Exchange. It is one of only two banks that has been part of the index (which includes just 19 companies) since inception. This year, the index has seen one newcomer, JSW S.A.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 31, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Poland: Citi Handlowy Named in the RESPECT Index for the Fifth Consecutive Year","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/poland-citi-handlowy-named-in-the-respect-index-for-the-fifth-consecutive-year","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Warsaw, Poland - The Citi Handlowy Benefits and Privileges Card was designed with the needs of our most demanding clients in mind. Beginning in July 2012, 'Benefits and Privileges Card' holders can enjoy a 10 percent discount when purchasing a new Audi car.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 31, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Handlowy Benefits and Privileges Card with New Features","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-handlowy-benefits-and-privileges-card-with-new-features","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Citi was recently named the winner of the Consumer Rights and Quality Service Prize in the Financial Literacy and Openness category by the Russian Chamber of Commerce and Industry in their 3rd Annual awards ceremony.","image":"638e31b0a3c47c530c0a6245","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 31, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi Russia Wins Consumer Rights and Quality Service Award","author.jobTitle":["Retail Bank Head, Citibank Russia"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-russia-wins-consumer-rights-and-quality-service-award","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"07","author.displayName":["Sergey Korotkov"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"New York - Citi has been named a winner of the first-ever Work Life Legacy Military Award. Families and Work Institute (FWI), a nonprofit research organization, created this award in response to the growing workforce challenge and opportunity facing servicemembers, their families and employers. Citi will be formally honored September 19, 2012, at FWI's annual Work Life Legacy Award dinner at Cipriani 42nd Street in New York City.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 30, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"U.S.: Citi Recognized for Supporting Transitioning Servicemembers and Their Families","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/us-citi-recognied-for-supporting-transitioning-servicemembers-and-their-families","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Pakistan - To inspire the business community to follow the lead taken by businesses in the area of sustainability, the United Nations Global Compact Pakistan Network has awarded Citi Pakistan for its 'Best Practices in Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR).' This recognition comes on the heels of three other recent global CSR awards that Citi Pakistan has won during 2011 and 2012.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 30, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Pakistan Awarded for 'Best Practices in CSR' by United Nations Global Compact Pakistan Network","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-pakistan-awarded-for-best-practices-in-csr-by-united-nations-global-compact-pakistan-network","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Last year, <a href=\"https://cfed.org/blog/inclusiveeconomy/spotlight_on_innovation_opportunity_funds_new_take_on_traditional_ida_programs/\">Opportunity Fund launched our newest savings product - Start2Save</a>. These savings accounts are designed to support low-income people in building up emergency savings through a free Citi savings account coupled with financial training and a matching grant of up to $1,000. Once a saver has earned the grant, how they use the money is completely up to them - no strings attached.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Gwendy Donaker Brown"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 30, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"It is time to Start2Save!","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Policy and New Initiatives, Opportunity Fund"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/it-is-time-to-start2save","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"As parents struggle to save enough to cover rising college costs, they need all the help they can get--including help from the taxman. Got money you want to sock away for your children's education? Here are three tax-advantaged accounts to consider.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 30, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Saving for College -- With a Little Help From the IRS","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/saving-for-college--with-a-little-help-from-the-irs","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Manama - Citibank, N.A., Bahrain's consumer business recently launched the Premium Account, a personalized solution with a touch of innovation.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 29, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Bahrain: Citibank Launches Premium Accounts","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/bahrain-citibank-launches-premium-accounts","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Caracas, Venezuela - On Friday, July 27, 82 participants from the Petare Training Center received their certificates at the closing event of the joint Citibank-SUPERATEC Banking and Finance Education Program, held at Citibank's N.A. Venezuela Branch.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 27, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Venezuela: Citi Promotes Closing Event of Joint Superatec Banking and Finance Education Program","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/veneuela-citi-promotes-closing-event-of-joint-superatec-banking-and-finance-education-program","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"The third installment of a special financial inclusion series underwritten by the Citi Foundation will debut this evening on the PBS weekly public affairs news program \"<a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/05/with-citi-foundation-support-pbs-spotlights-financial-inclusion.shtml\">Need to Know</a>\". The five-part series, \"Your Money and Your Life,\" illustrates the Citi Foundation's commitment to educate, empower and transform low-income communities by supporting efforts to build financial capability among consumers. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/05/with-citi-foundation-support-pbs-spotlights-financial-inclusion.shtml\">Click here to read a previous post about the series' debut. </a>","image":"638e3100a3c47c530c0a5f23","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 27, 2012","type":"insights","title":"PBS series supported by the Citi Foundation focuses next on the financial decisions facing the working poor","author.jobTitle":["Citi Foundation Program Officer"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/pbs-series-supported-by-the-citi-foundation-focuses-next-on-the-financial-decisions-facing-the-worki","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"07","author.displayName":["Daria Sheehan"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 19th installation below covers how the profile of National City Bank's employees evolved in the 1950's and 60's, becoming more diverse. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/07/citi-turns-200-pioneers-in-a-mans-world.shtml\">Read the 18th installment on the success of female employees in Brazil and Columbia forecasts the importance of women in banking, here</a>.","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 27, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: New Hiring and Training Practices Bring Greater Diversity","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-new-hiring-and-training-practices-bring-greater-diversity","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"São Paulo - The 2014 FIFA World Cup, the 2016 Olympic Games as well as the growing wealth and urbanization of Brazil are placing unprecedented demands on the nation's infrastructure. According to the Brazilian Association of Infrastructure and Basic Industries (ABDIB), an average investment of $110 billion per year will be needed over the next five years. How to meet the country and region's pressing infrastructure needs was the main topic of discussion at the FT/Citi Ingenuity Awards Infrastructure Forum held today in São Paulo.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 26, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Experts Optimistic That Brazil Can Meet Growing Demands on its Infrastructure","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/experts-optimistic-that-brail-can-meet-growing-demands-on-its-infrastructure","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - Citibank Hungary's new Debt Consolidation Loan offers consumers an outstanding opportunity to consolidate multiple loans, including personal loans, overdrafts, durable goods financing and credit cards from various financial institutions into one Personal Installment Loan from Citibank. The annual interest rate of the Citibank Debt Consolidation Loan is 19.9 percent for applications submitted via all channels, including branches, direct sales agents, telephone and online, and may result in a reduction of the customers' earlier monthly installments by up to 25 to 30 percent.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 26, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Hungary Introduces 19.9 Percent Interest Rate Debt Consolidation Loan","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-hungary-introduces-199-percent-interest-rate-debt-consolidation-loan","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"The US Citi Economic Surprise Index is at levels that suggest potential inflection from a low point. While the CESI has been lower in the past (such as in mid-2011 and late 2008), there are some signs that it may be in the process of bottoming given the model's inherent mean reversion characteristic. While disappointing releases such as the June ISM figure arguably should have pushed the index down meaningfully, it did not as a result of generally lowered broad expectations. <br><br>The G10 Global CESI also looks to be near a trough. While the G10 surprise index's correlation with stock price movement is somewhat higher than the US CESI, this may reflect the impact of global growth forecasts on aggregate stock price trends. Indeed, barring the 2008-09 Great Recession period, the global CESI looks to be at a bottom if history is any guide. <br><br>Markets tend to be tied most closely to actuality relative to projections rather than in absolute terms. With reduced forecasts and the realization that most investors already are deeply worried about European economic woes, the US fiscal cliff and China's slowdown, economists and analysts have been trimming back GDP and earnings estimates, respectively. Hence, the hurdle rates have come down to a point that generates an opportunity for stock prices to appreciate rather than slide.","image":"638e31b6a3c47c530c0a6262","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 26, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Equity Strategy: July 2012 Chart of the Month","author.jobTitle":["Chief US Equity Strategist, Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/equity-strategy-july-chart-of-the-month","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"07","author.displayName":["Tobias Levkovich"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Shanghai, China - Citi was ranked by business students as the employer of choice among foreign banks in China, according to the latest IDEAL survey. The survey was conducted by Globe Biweekly Magazine and Universum, a leading human resources company.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 25, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Ranked Most Attractive Employer Among Foreign Banks in China","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-ranked-most-attractive-employer-among-foreign-banks-in-china","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"In a recent appearance on Bloomberg's \"The Next Big Trade\", Citi Multi-Industry & Electrical Equipment Analyst, Deane Dray, speaks on high-end investment opportunities in water. He says in part:","image":"638e31b7a3c47c530c0a6269","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 25, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Analyst Deane Dray Speaks on Investing in Liquid Assets","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-analyst-deane-dray-speaks-on-investing-in-liquid-assets","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Hong Kong - Leveraging the success of last year's pilot program, which received an overwhelming response from commercial bank clients and their children, Citibank is launching the second Youth Leadership Program this year exclusively for the next generation of children, aged 16-19, of Citi Commercial Bank's clients. The program, a collaboration between Citibank and Institute for Entrepreneurship (IfE), The Hong Kong Polytechnic University, aims at providing quality leadership and entrepreneurship training to scions of successful businesses and instilling in them a passion and desire to become future business leaders.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Launches Second Youth Leadership Program Fostering Scions of Commercial Bank Clients to be Leaders of Next Generation","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-launches-second-youth-leadership-program-fostering-scions-of-commercial-bank-clients-to-be-leaders-of-next-generation","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"Citi once again won the nod for the Best Foreign Commercial Bank in the Philippines, for the 14th consecutive year, in <i>FinanceAsia's</i> annual Country Awards for Achievement 2012. Hong Kong-based <i>FinanceAsia</i>, a leading financial publication in Asia, recognizes the best financial services firms in each country across the region with this award.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Philippines Named Best Foreign Bank by FinanceAsia","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-philippines-named-best-foreign-bank-by-financeasia","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"McLean, Va. and New York - Delivering a better experience wherever travelers pay and stay globally, Citi and Hilton HHonors, the loyalty program for Hilton Worldwide's 10 distinct hotel brands, introduced today the Citi® Hilton HHonors Reserve Visa Signature® Card. The new card offers multiple ways to earn HHonors Bonus points on everyday purchases and an annual weekend night certificate good at over 3,800 hotels and resorts within the Hilton Worldwide portfolio. International travelers can travel with ease and enjoy global acceptance with their Citi Hilton HHonors Reserve Card through advanced chip technology, no foreign purchase transaction fees and worldwide recognition of the Visa brand.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi® and Hilton Honors Worldwide Introduce New Citi® Hilton HHonors™ Reserve Credit Card","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-and-hilton-honors-worldwide-introduce-new-citi-hilton-hhonors-reserve-credit-card","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Investors are often described as risk averse, meaning they favor certificates of deposit, high-quality bonds and other more conservative investments. Yet many of us aren't really risk averse. Rather, we are loss averse--meaning we hate losing money--and that can sometimes prompt us to take on more risk.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 23, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Risk Aversion vs. Loss Aversion","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/risk-aversion-vs-loss-aversion","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Citi and Habitat for Humanity recently launched the Citi-Habitat Home Improvement Microsavings Program in the Philippines, a regional initiative which aims to help 3,000 low-income homeowners save a total of US$2 million to strengthen their homes against natural disasters.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 20, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Philippines and Habitat for Humanity Launch Home Improvement Microsavings Program","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-philippines-and-habitat-for-humanity-launch-home-improvement-microsavings-program","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup today announced that it has been selected to receive the 2012 Secretary of Defense Employer Support Freedom Award by the Employer Support of the Guard and Reserve (ESGR), a Department of Defense (DoD) agency. Fifteen employers will be honored with this year's Freedom Award, the DoD's highest recognition given to employers for exceptional support of Guard and Reserve employees. Citi is the only bank to receive the 2012 Freedom Award. These recipients distinguished themselves among the 3,236 nominations submitted earlier this year by Guardsmen and Reservists, or family members acting on their behalf. Thirty employee-service members nominated Citi for the award.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 20, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"DoD Names Citi as 2012 Secretary of Defense Employer Support Freedom Award Recipient","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/dod-names-citi-as-2012-secretary-of-defense-employer-support-freedom-award-recipient","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/rcs/citigpa/storage/public/Proud%20Recipient%20of%20the%20Freedom%20Award%20Logo.jpg\"></a>Citi is honored to announce that we have been selected to receive the 2012 Secretary of Defense Employer Support Freedom Award by the <a href=\"https://www.esgr.org/site/\">Employer Support of the Guard and Reserve</a> (ESGR), a <a href=\"https://www.defense.gov/\">Department of Defense</a> (DoD) agency. The Freedom Award is the DoD's highest recognition given to employers for exceptional support of Guard and Reserve employees. Citi is the only bank to receive the 2012 Freedom Award.","image":"638e31b9a3c47c530c0a6274","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 20, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi named 2012 Secretary of Defense Employer Support Freedom Award Recipient by Department of Defense","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-named-2012-secretary-of-defense-employer-support-freedom-award-recipient-by-department-of-defen","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 18th installation below covers how the success of female employees in Brazil and Columbia forecasts the importance of women in banking. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/07/citi-turns-200-walter-wriston-joins-the-team.shtml\">Read the 17th installment on how Walter Wriston helped revitalize the bank's overseas division, here.</a>","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 20, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Pioneers in a Man's World","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-pioneers-in-a-mans-world","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Washington, D.C. - The Multilateral Investment Guarantee Agency (MIGA)-the political risk insurance arm of the World Bank Group-today announced it is supporting the government of Panama's efforts to construct a modern and integrated mass-transit system as a solution to Panama City's urban transportation issues. In connection with the financing plan for this ambitious new infrastructure investment, MIGA has issued a guarantee of $320 million to cover a $250 million loan arranged by Citi Transaction Services and Citigroup Global Markets, Inc. (Citi), including interest and other financing costs associated with the construction of Line 1 of the metro system. This project represents MIGA's first coverage of non-honoring of sovereign financial obligations in Latin America and the Caribbean.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 19, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"MIGA Guarantee Backs Panama City Metro Line","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/miga-guarantee-backs-panama-city-metro-line","tags":["Press Release Migration"]},{"summary":"San José, Costa Rica - Citi, the Citi Foundation and the ADRI Association announced the opening of nominations for the sixth annual Citi Microentrepreneurship Awards in Costa Rica.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 19, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Costa Rica: Citi Opens Nominations for Its Sixth Annual Microentrepreneurship Award","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/costa-rica-citi-opens-nominations-for-its-sixth-annual-microentrepreneurship-award","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"The Indo-American Corporate Excellence Awards 2012 hosted by The Indo-American Chamber of Commerce (IACC), recently awarded Citi India as the 'Best US Company in India in Financial Services'. The Indo-American Corporate Excellence Awards celebrate corporate excellence and recognize the best US companies in India and Indian companies in the US. Citi India was awarded this recognition based on its uniqueness in Human Capital Management, Corporate Social Responsibility and overall contribution to Indo-US business.","image":"638e31bda3c47c530c0a6289","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 19, 2012","type":"insights","title":"Citi Awarded Best US Company in India in Financial Services by The Indo-American Chamber of Commerce","author.jobTitle":["Citi Country Officer, India"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-awarded-best-us-company-in-india-in-financial-services-by-the-indo-american-chamber-of-commerce","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"07","author.displayName":["Pramit Jhaveri"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"Lima, Peru - Citibank Peru, a leading participant in the Peruvian financial system with more than 92 years of uninterrupted presence in the market, announced today the seventh edition of the Citi Microenterprise Award, PREMIC 2012, in partnership with IPAE Acción Empresarial and the Citi Foundation.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Peru: Citi Announces the Opening of the Seventh Annual Citi Microenterprise Award, PREMIC 2012","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/peru-citi-announces-the-opening-of-the-seventh-annual-citi-microenterprise-award-premic-2012","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Seoul, Korea - Citi Card has become very popular due to its premium dining service that provides a 10 percent discount or free menu items at nearly 1,000 restaurants. Recently, Citi Card launched an official Facebook page (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/citikorea\" target=\"blank\">www.facebook.com/citikorea</a>) and hosted several events that offered dining, ice cream and coffee gift coupons to 2,012 participants.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Korea: Citi Card Launches Facebook Page and Introduces Ways to Enjoy Premium Dining Service","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/korea-citi-card-launches-facebook-page-and-introduces-ways-to-enjoy-premium-dining-service","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - The Board of Directors of Citigroup Inc. today declared a quarterly dividend on the company's common stock of $0.01 per share, payable on August 24, 2012 to stockholders of record on August 6, 2012.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Declares Dividends","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-declares-dividends-12","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Bangkok - Citi Thailand has been named Thailand's Best Foreign Commercial Bank for 2012 by <i>FinanceAsia</i> magazine, one of Asia's leading financial trade publications. This marks the 10th consecutive year that Citi Thailand has won this highly respected award.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Thailand Named Best Foreign Commercial Bank for 10th Consecutive Year","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-thailand-named-best-foreign-commercial-bank-for-10th-consecutive-year","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Celebrating Citi's 200 years of global experience, Citibank Romania reconfirms its unparalleled client focus through the launch of a creative and responsible financial solution.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 18, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"All Inclusive - The Latest Comprehensive Current Account Package from Citibank Romania","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/all-inclusive--the-latest-comprehensive-current-account-package-from-citibank-romania","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Last fall, Citi employees, individuals and groups of up to 300, came together to leverage the diverse musical talents in celebration of <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/tagsearch?tag=Citi200\">Citi's 200th anniversary</a>. The variety of performances ran the gamut - many put together dance routines with coworkers, others sang at home, and some even showed off their beat-boxing skills. It was amazing to see the performances roll in from across the globe. Each employee brought a new musical style to the table, and we were constantly amazed by their spirit and musical talent. It was a wonderful representation of the great diversity within Citi.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Art Tildesley"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 17, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Creates a Global Citi® Music Video to Commemorate the 200th Anniversary","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Head of Global Executive Services and Citi Volunteers"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-creates-a-global-citi-music-video-to-commemorate-the-200th-anniversary","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Budapest, Hungary - On July 10, 14 representatives of 12 social enterprises from the NESsT-Citibank Social Enterprise Development Programs participated in an interactive roundtable discussion with Citi's Consumer Bank CEO for EMEA, Marc Luet. The aim of this roundtable was to provide an opportunity for the leaders of social enterprises to hear from a globally recognized business leader about building a sustainable social enterprise. The other goals of the forum were for participants to learn from Marc Luet about the attributes of a sustainable enterprise through his personal experiences and for them to have the opportunity to ask him questions.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Representatives of 12 Social Enterprises from the NESsT-Citibank Social Enterprise Development Programs Participated in an Interactive Roundtable Discussion with Citi's EMEA Consumer Bank CEO Marc Luet","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/representatives-of-12-social-enterprises-from-the-nesst-citibank-social-enterprise-development-programs-participated-in-an-interactive-roundtable-discussion-with-citi-s-emea-consumer-bank-ceo-marc-luet","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup Inc. today reported net income for the second quarter 2012 of $2.9 billion, or $0.95 per diluted share, on revenues of $18.6 billion.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Reports Second Quarter 2012 Earnings per Share of $0.95; $1.00 Excluding the Impact of Positive CVA/DVA and a Net Loss on the Sale of a 10.1% Stake in Akbank T.A.S.","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-reports-second-quarter-2012-earnings-per-share-of-095-100-excluding-the-impact-of-positive-cvadva-and-a-net-loss-on-the-sale-of-a-101-stake-in-akbank-tas","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Hong Kong - Citi has been awarded the title of Best Bank in Asia by the editors of <i>Euromoney</i> magazine. Citi also picked up best Cash Management Bank in Asia, Best Investment Bank in Indonesia and Best Equity House in India. The awards were announced in Hong Kong on July 12.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Named Euromoney's Best Bank in Asia","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-named-euromoney-s-best-bank-in-asia","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"After decades in the workforce, it can be unnerving to retire and give up that regular paycheck. What to do? Consider bundling together different sources of retirement income so you have at least enough cash coming in to cover core living expenses, such as utilities, groceries, taxes, insurance and any rent or mortgage. That way, you can be fairly confident you can cover the bills, even if the financial markets go through a rocky spell.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Putting a Floor Under Your Retirement Income","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/putting-a-floor-under-your-retirement-income","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Earlier this morning, Citi released its earnings report for the second quarter of 2012. Chief Financial Officer John Gerspach discusses the report in this video. For more information and the full earnings report, visit the <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/global/investors\">Investor Relations</a> section of Citigroup's website.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 16, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Releases Second Quarter 2012 Earnings","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-releases-second-quarter-2012-earnings"},{"summary":"Warsaw - For five years, as part of the \"Wiecej drzew dzieki Tobie\" (\"More Trees, Thanks to You\") program, Citi Handlowy has encouraged its customers to give up paper statements and agree to receiving statements in electronic form. Thanks to this, 520,000 trees have already been planted! An application on the CitiMobile profile was launched this month promoting such pro-environmental initiatives.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Poland: Plant Your Tree with Citi Handlowy - Now Also on Facebook","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/poland-plant-your-tree-with-citi-handlowy-now-also-on-facebook","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Sofia - Citibank Bulgaria was named Best Foreign Bank Branch in Bulgaria for 2011 by the Bulgarian Bank of the Year Association. The Bulgarian franchise is recognized for its performance for the second consecutive year. The prestigious award was presented at a high-profile ceremony attended by many in the Bulgarian banking community, the Central Bank Governor and representatives of other regulatory bodies, government officials, business and the media.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Bulgaria Named Best Foreign Bank Branch in Bulgaria","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-bulgaria-named-best-foreign-bank-branch-in-bulgaria","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Candi Wolff, Citi Executive Vice President of Government Affairs, was recently named one of Washington D.C.'s 25 most influential women by <a href=\"https://influencealley.nationaljournal.com/2012/07/washingtons-25-top-influential.php\">National Journal</a>.","image":"638e31c1a3c47c530c0a62a0","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi's Candi Wolff Named One of 25 Most Influential Women in Washington D.C.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citis-candi-wolff-named-one-of-25-most-influential-women-in-washington-dc","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"<a href=\"https://bitc.org.uk/\">Business in the Community (BITC)</a> awarded Citi this year's International Award for demonstrating that financial inclusion is embedded in our core business with a clear sense of social purpose.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Francesco Vanni d'Archirafi","Bob Annibale"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Scaling microfinance to reach the underserved in communities around the world","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["CEO of Citi Holdings and Chairman of the Board of Governors of Junior Achievement Worldwide","Citi Pride Affinity Co-lead"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/scaling-microfinance-to-reach-the-underserved-in-communities-around-the-world","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"In celebration of Citigroup's 200th Anniversary, we are sharing stories from our rich history here on this blog. The 17th installation below covers how Walter Wriston helped revitalize the bank's overseas division. <a href=\"https://blog.citigroup.com/2012/07/citi-turns-200-expansion-plans-for-bank-abroad.shtml\">Read the 16th installment on how George Moore helped National City Bank plan for additional expansion abroad, here</a>.","image":"638e30faa3c47c530c0a5f05","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 13, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Turns 200: Walter Wriston Joins the Team","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-turns-200-walter-wriston-joins-the-team","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"São Paulo - A partnership between Citi Brazil and the Brazilian Medical Association (AMB) brings with it a series of exclusive benefits for physicians. The promotion is valid for medical professionals who open a Citi account between May 2 and December 31, 2012. Doctors do not have to be affiliated with the AMB to be eligible for the Citibank benefits; the only requirement is to apply for a checking account at a Citi branch and activate it within two months of its approval (see terms and conditions).","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Brazil: Citi Offers Line of Credit of up to R$ 750,000 for Doctors","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/brail-citi-offers-line-of-credit-of-up-to-r-750000-for-doctors","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup Inc. is announcing the redemption of a series of Citi trust preferred securities - the 7.250% Enhanced T<sub>RU</sub>PS® issued by Citigroup Capital XIX (CUSIP: 17311U200) (the \"ET<sub>RU</sub>PS®\"). The ET<sub>RU</sub>PS® are being redeemed, along with the common securities issued by Citigroup Capital XIX and held by Citi, as a result of the concurrent redemption in whole by Citi of the junior subordinated debt securities held by Citigroup Capital XIX which underlie the ET<sub>RU</sub>PS®.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Announces Redemption of Trust Preferred Securities Issued by Citigroup Capital XIX","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citigroup-announces-redemption-of-trust-preferred-securities-issued-by-citigroup-capital-xix","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"In light of recent events impacting client asset protection, customers are increasingly concerned about the protection of their collateral, and clearing members' controls and policies around safeguarding client money. To aid this concern, Citi recently launched its Client Segregation Transparency Initiative, which provides clients unparalleled access into Citi's collateral segregation processes for Futures and Cleared OTC products. Clients are now provided daily insight via Citi Velocity into the amount of Futures and cleared OTC collateral Citi is holding, custodial locations, and breakdown of collateral investments.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Christopher Perkins"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 12, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Launches Client Segregation Transparency Initiative","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Global Head of OTC Clearing, Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-launches-client-segregation-transparency-initiative-1","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi today launched its Client Segregation Transparency Initiative, which provides clients unparalleled access into Citi's collateral segregation processes for Futures and Cleared OTC products.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 11, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Launches Client Segregation Transparency Initiative","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-launches-client-segregation-transparency-initiative","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"The NCLR Lead the Way conference, which several of my Citi colleagues and I attended this week, is a great opportunity to meet friends and colleagues and discuss issues that are important to our nation's economically vulnerable families and communities. On Monday, I was privileged to participate in \"<a href=\"https://www.nclr.org/index.php/events/nclr_annual_conference-1/workshops/town_halls/\">Don't Quit the Dream: A Vision for Homeownership Beyond 2012</a>,\" a town hall along with leaders from the government and nonprofit sectors. Like Citi, each of them is committed to achieving long-term affordable homeownership, particularly for low- and moderate-income families.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Natalie Abatemarco"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 11, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"The Future of Housing: Economic growth and opportunity for all","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Managing Director, Citi Community Development"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/the-future-of-housing-economic-growth-and-opportunity-for-all","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Warsaw - Citi Handlowy's \"Wakacje w obiektywie\" (Holidays on Camera) competition for Citibank credit cards holders has begun. Customers who regularly use their cards can win Samsung Galaxy S III phones and sets of books by Beata Pawlikowska. In addition, the winners will meet with the famous traveler.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Poland: \"Wakacje w obiektywie\" (Holidays on Camera), Citi Handlowy's New Competition","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/poland-wakacje-w-obiektywie-holidays-on-camera-citi-handlowy-s-new-competition","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"A recent Citi survey revealed that just 41 percent of people making less than $50,000 a year are saving on a regular basis. Only a quarter of them say they have savings goals or feel they are saving enough. Also, the <a href=\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/pubs/bulletin/2012/PDF/scf12.pdf\">Federal Reserve Board's Survey of Consumer Finances for 2010</a> shows that the median net worth of Americans fell 39 percent, from $126,400 in 2007 to $77,300 in 2010. This represents a whopping loss of wealth and financial security for all Americans, and the data is even more daunting for low-income and minority communities.","month":"07","author.displayName":["Sandy Fernandez"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"The Asset Building Policy Network: How can we support a savings culture?","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Senior Vice President, Citi Community Development"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/the-asset-building-policy-network-how-can-we-support-a-savings-culture","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"As we strive to amass enough for retirement, we need to make assumptions about our likely investment returns. The risk: Our return assumptions are too high--and we end up saving too little or betting heavily on the wrong investments. Want to avoid those mistakes? Here are a few pointers:","month":"07","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"July 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"What Investment Returns Can We Expect?","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/what-investment-returns-can-we-expect","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Guatemala City - For the seventh consecutive year and as part of Citi's commitment to developing microenterprise, the Citi Foundation, with the support of the Network of Guatemalan Microfinance Institutions (REDIMIF), announced the launch of the Citi Microentrepreneurship Awards, Guatemala 2012.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 07, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Launches Seventh Annual Microentrepreneurship Award in Guatemala","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2012/citi-launches-seventh-annual-microentrepreneurship-award-in-guatemala","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"London - <i>Euromoney</i>, the preeminent global financial markets magazine, recognized Citi as \"Best Global Emerging Markets Investment Bank\" and \"Best Global Transaction Banking House\" at its annual Awards for Excellence ceremony last evening in London.","month":"07","year":"2012","publishDate":"July 06, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Euromoney Taps Citi as Top Emerging Markets and Transaction Banking House","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/euromoney-taps-citi-as-top-emerging-markets-and-transaction-banking-house","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Miami, Florida - Citi gained recognition for its investment banking division in Latin America with the announcement that <i>Euromoney</i> has awarded it <a href=\"http://www.euromoney.com/Article/3054979/Caribbean-Awards-for-Excellence-2012-By-country.html#a\" target=\"blank\">Best Investment Bank in the Caribbean</a> for the third consecutive year in the <i>Euromoney</i> Awards for Excellence. The award wa