/news/perspective/2012/evaluation-in-action-demonstrating-results-measuring-impact-and-informing-change-in-financial-capabi","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Warsaw - Beginning Monday, March 26, residents of Warsaw who decide to open a CitiOne account may benefit from the \"Park with Citi Handlowy\" promotion. As part of the promotion they will get the Warsaw City Debit Card topped up with the amount of PLN 50 to be used at parking meters of Warsaw Non-Guarded Parking Toll Zone.","month":"04","year":"2012","publishDate":"April 03, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Park with Citi Handlowy","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/park-with-citi-handlowy","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citi today announced that Rohan Weerasinghe will join the company as its General Counsel and Corporate Secretary. Michael Helfer, who has been General Counsel and Corporate Secretary for nine years, will become Vice Chairman. Both appointments are effective June 1.","month":"04","year":"2012","publishDate":"April 03, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Appoints Rohan Weerasinghe General Counsel","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-appoints-rohan-weerasinghe-general-counsel","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York, and Ft. Worth, Texas - Directly responding to the rewards and recognition that travelers want, Citi and American Airlines introduced seven new benefits to the Citi® Platinum Select® / AAdvantage® card, including 10 percent miles back on American Airlines AAdvantage® miles redeemed, up to 10,000 miles per calendar year, free first checked bag, priority boarding and more.","month":"04","year":"2012","publishDate":"April 02, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi and American Airlines Announce the New Citi® Platinum Select® / AA