ate":"March 06, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Bahrain Launches the New PremierMiles Visa Credit Card","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-bahrain-launches-the-new-premiermiles-visa-credit-card","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Your 401(k) plan is supposed to help pay for retirement. But should you also use it to cover financial emergencies, foot the kids' tuition bills and pay for home improvements?","month":"03","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2012","publishDate":"March 06, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Pros and Cons of 401(k) Loans","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/pros-and-cons-of-401k-loans","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Mumbai - Citibank India today announced the launch of 'Citibanking,' a new retail banking proposition for consumers in India. Citibanking will offer unprecedented global access, increased convenience, connectivity and personalization for everyday banking needs. It is designed for customers who are upwardly mobile and maintain a relationship value of a minimum INR 200,000 with the bank.","month":"03","year":"2012","publishDate":"March 05, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank India Launches New Value Proposition","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-india-launches-new-value-proposition","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Armonk, New York/New York, New York - Citigroup (NYSE: C) today announced it has entered into an agreement with IBM (NYSE: IBM) to explore possible uses for IBM Watson. Under the agreement, Citi will examine the use of deep content analysis and evidence based learning capabilities found in IB