.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citibank-thailand-opens-third-branch-at-centralworld-shopping-complex","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"This week, Citibank (China) Co. Ltd. (\"Citi\") announced that it has received approval from the China Banking Regulatory Commission to launch a credit card business in China. The business will encompass both retail and commercial cards, and is expected to be launched sometime in 2012.","month":"02","year":"2012","publishDate":"February 10, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Receives Approval to Launch Credit Cards in China","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2012/citi-receives-approval-to-launch-credit-cards-in-china-1","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"San Francisco - Nearly half of Californians believe 2012 will be better than 2011, according to the latest Citi California Pulse®, a sign that the state's residents are increasingly optimistic about the coming year. Thirty-three percent expect this year to be about the same as last year, and only 17 percent say it will be worse.","month":"02","year":"2012","publishDate":"February 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi California Pulse® Survey: Nearly Half of Californians Believe 2012 will be Better than 2011","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2012/citi-california-pulse-survey-nearly-half-of-californians-believe-2012-will-be-better-than-2011","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup Inc. today issued the following statement on the agreement in principle on residential loan servicing and origination practices:","month":"02","year":"2012","publishDate":"February 09, 2012","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Statement on Agreement in Principle on Residential Loan Servicing and Origination Practices","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url