nior Bankers Congress at the Washington Sycip Development Center in Makati City. As one of the citizenship initiatives of Citi geared towards youth education, the program aims to provide college students with first-hand knowledge into the banking and finance sector and eventually link participants to mentorships and job placements with FINEX member companies. Citi Junior Bankers Congress is funded by the Citi Foundation.","month":"12","year":"2011","publishDate":"December 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Philippines: Citi, FINEX Foundation Launch the Ninth Citi Junior Bankers Congress","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/philippines-citi-finex-foundation-launch-the-ninth-citi-junior-bankers-congress","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup will issue its fourth quarter results via press release at approximately 8:00 AM (EST) on Tuesday, January 17, 2012. At 10:30 AM (EST), results will be reviewed via live webcast and teleconference.","month":"12","year":"2011","publishDate":"December 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Fourth Quarter 2011 Earnings Review","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-fourth-quarter-2011-earnings-review","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Along with the arrival of 2012 come some key changes in the IRS limits that affect our financial lives. Got a 401(k)? If you're under age 50, you can contribute a maximum $17,000 in 2012, up from this year's $16,500 limit.","month":"12","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"December 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Next Year by the Numbers","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspec