ic Teams","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-team-usa-flag-tour-stops-in-tucson-to-celebrate-sponsorship-of-2012-us-olympic-paralympic-teams","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"New York - On October 19, 2011, Citigroup Inc. announced the declaration by its Board of Directors of a dividend of $0.01 per share of common stock payable on November 23, 2011 to holders of record on November 7, 2011. Effective on the payment of this dividend, an adjustment will be made to the settlement rates and certain other terms of Citi's T-DECS, as set forth below. No adjustment will be made to the terms of Citi's warrants or convertible preferred stock because the amount of the dividend to be paid is less than the threshold amount required for an adjustment. You should refer to the T-DECS Prospectus dated December 16, 2009 and the related Current Report on Form 8-K filed on December 24, 2009 for the definitions of the terms below and for other relevant provisions of the T-DECS.","month":"11","year":"2011","publishDate":"November 08, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Inc. Announces T-DECS Adjustments to Result from Common Dividend","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citigroup-inc-announces-t-decs-adjustments-to-result-from-common-dividend-1","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"In a new <a href=\"https://blog.womenandco.com/2011/11/hey-mom-dad-can-i-see-your-checkbook.html\">blog post</a>, Women & Co.'s President & CEO Linda Descano discusses how you can open a dialogue with your parents about helping them organize their financial plans, wills, health care proxies, living wills, etc. and prepare for the future.","month":"11","year":"2011","publishDate":"November 08, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"On the Women & Co. Blog: Hey Mom & Dad, Can I See Your Checkbook?","category":"PERSPECTIVES","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/on-the-women-co-blog-hey-mom-dad-can-i-see-your-checkbook-1","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Sao Paulo - <a href=\"http://www.credicard.com.br/\">Credicard</a> and <a href=\"http://www.laramara.org.br/\">Laramara NGO</a>, a Brazilian Association that provides assistance to the visually impaired, signed a partnership to facilitate the acquisition of accessibility equipment for people who are blind or have low vision, such as magnifiers, Braille machines, text-to-speech software, voice canes, thermometers and pressure gauges, among other products.","month":"11","year":"2011","publishDate":"November 07, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Credicard Launches Special Line of Credit to Purchase Equipment for Blind And Low-Vision People In Brazil","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/credicard-launches-special-line-of-credit-to-purchase-equipment-for-blind-and-low-vision-people-in-brail","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Miami, Florida - Citi announced that Manuel Medina-Mora has expanded his role and was appointed CEO Global Consumer and Commercial Banking. This appointment aims at better positioning Citi to consolidate its sustainable growth.","month":"11","year":"2011","publishDate":"November 07, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Manuel Medina-Mora Expands His Role and Is Appointed Chief Executive Officer for Global Consumer Banking","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/manuel-medina-mora-expands-his-role-and-is-appointed-chief-executive-officer-for-global-consumer-banking","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Bucharest - Citibank Romania customers can now benefit from the most convenient way to send and receive money to and from Citibank individual accounts across 29 countries, through the newly launched Citibank Global Transfers service.","month":"11","year":"2011","publishDate":"November 07, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Launches Global Transfers - The Most Convenient Way to Send and Receive Money Across 29 Countries Around the World","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citibank-launches-global-transfers--the-most-convenient-way-to-send-and-receive-money-across-29-countries-around-the-world","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"We're often advised to put away a little money every month. This approach works well for those of us in the work force. We get our paychecks and immediately turn around and add a little to our savings. If our employer offers a 401(k) plan, this regular saving might even be automatic, with our 401(k) contributions pulled out of our income and stashed directly in the investments we choose.","month":"11","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"November 07, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Dollar-Cost averaging","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/dollar-cost-averaging","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Citi and Dakotas America recently partnered to allocate over $42 Million in new markets tax credit financing and Citi Community Capital lending to expand the Rockyford and Batesland Schools on the Lakota Pine Ridge Indian Reservation in South Dakota. The new facilities will increase the capacity of the schools to accommodate a growing population as well as provide modernized facilities and enhanced technology to improve the quality of education for some of America's neediest students. Pine Ridge has historically ranked as one of America's most impoverished communities.","m