his and later posts what my role involves on a project like this.","image":"638e2fd4a3c47c530c0a59b8","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 23, 2011","type":"insights","title":"From the British Museum and Citi: Small objects telling big stories.","author.jobTitle":["Interpretation Officer, British Museum"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/from-the-british-museum-and-citi-small-objects-telling-big-stories","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"09","author.displayName":["Anna Bright"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"New York – Citigroup is pleased to announce that its Chairman Richard Parsons, Board Member Judith Rodin and General Counsel and Corporate Secretary Michael Helfer have been named to the National Association of Corporate Directors' (NACD's) 2011 Directorship 100, in recognition of their work promoting the highest standards of corporate governance.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 22, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Directors, Executive Named to Prestigious 2011 NACD Directorship 100","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-directors-executive-named-to-prestigious-2011-nacd-directorship-100","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Citi Pakistan has introduced the first-of-its-kind prepaid card in the local market. The prepaid card is a payment solution through which an electronic account is pre-funded by a corporate client to be used by its employees. Individuals receiving payments will be able to use the prepaid card at point-of-sale terminals, or to draw their funds from ATMs across the country. This will in effect replace existing checks, vouchers or cash payments with a more efficient, secure and convenient Prepaid Visa Card.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 22, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Pakistan: Citi Pioneers the Launch of Prepaid Cards","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/pakistan-citi-pioneers-the-launch-of-prepaid-cards","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Philippe Jaccard, Asia Head for Liquidity and Investments, Global Transaction Services, Citi, <a href=\"https://www.citibank.com/transactionservices/home/corporations/industries/videos/philippe_li_video.jsp\">explains</a> how he helps clients expanding abroad to structure liquidity solutions, noting that emerging multinationals can incorporate the learnings of earlier multinational corporations to build efficiencies into their treasury management systems from the start. \"...They have a unique opportunity to leapfrog,\" he says.","image":"638e2fd8a3c47c530c0a59c5","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 22, 2011","type":"insights","title":"Jaccard: Developing multinationals have \"unique opportunity to leapfrog.\"","author.jobTitle":["Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/jaccard-developing-multinationals-have-unique-opportunity-to-leapfrog","tags":["Perspective Migration"],"month":"09","author.displayName":["Citi"],"siteId":"citigpa","category":"PERSPECTIVES"},{"summary":"\"Although we are pleased that Moody's affirmed both the long-term and short-term ratings of Citibank, N.A. and the long-term rating of Citigroup, we completely disagree with Moody's change to Citigroup's short-term rating. It does not accurately reflect the significant progress Citi has made since Moody's last rated Citi more than two-and-a-half years ago. Regardless, we believe that less than 1% of Citi's funding will be affected by the Moody's decision and the downgrade will not affect the short-term and long-term funding of our bank vehicles.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 21, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Statement on Moody's Announcement","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-statement-on-moody-s-announcement","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Citi has created a <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/citi/press/2011/110914a.htm\">new tool</a>-- the Citi On Campus App for iPhone -- to help students connect with some of our campus recruiting activities. Our campus recruiting team challenged Citi's technology group to move us beyond traditional methods of poster boards and handouts and attract students to our events using their preferred channels. This iPhone App is one result.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Eileen Stephan"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"September 21, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Introducing the Citi® On Campus App for iPhone.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Managing Director and Head of Campus Recruiting for Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/introducing-the-citi-on-campus-app-for-iphone-1","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"New York – <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/\">Citi</a>, in collaboration with <a href=\"http://www.edf.org/\">Environmental Defense Fund</a> (EDF), is convening a group of nearly 150 practitioners on energy efficiency finance today to explore opportunities on how to build and scale the energy efficiency financing market. At the event, Citi will be announcing its goal to develop and replicate a suite of solutions that will direct significant financing for energy efficiency retrofits over the next 18-24 months.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Collaborates with Environmental Defense Fund to Co-host Innovations in Energy Efficiency Financing Conference","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-collaborates-with-environmental-defense-fund-to-co-host-innovations-in-energy-efficiency-financing-conference","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Toronto & New York - Citi today announced the launch of a new web-based supply chain platform for 14 countries in Latin America. This builds on Citi's global supply chain offerings which have been recognized as best of class by Global Finance Magazine in its awards of \"Best Global Supply Chain Finance Provider\" as well as \"Best in Latin America and North America.\" The 14 countries include Brazil, Mexico, Peru, Argentina, Colombia, Panama, Puerto Rico, Dominican Republic, Costa Rica, El Salvador, Guatemala, Honduras, Jamaica and Trinidad.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Latin America: Citi's Global Transactions Services Launches Innovative Web-Based Regional Supply Chain Finance Solution","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/latin-america-citi-s-global-transactions-services-launches-innovative-web-based-regional-supply-chain-finance-solution","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"Citi today announced a commitment of $24 billion in lending over the next three years - $7 billion in 2011, $8 billion in 2012 and $9 billion in 2013. The announcement comes in conjunction with recent efforts by the U.S. Small Business Administration (SBA) to provide access to lending and capital that will help create jobs and speed economic recovery.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Commits to Lending $24 Billion to American Small Businesses Over the Next Three Years","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-commits-to-lending-24-billion-to-american-small-businesses-over-the-next-three-years","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Today, Citi announced our commitment to lend American businesses $24 billion over the next three years. We're proud to do our part in answering the U.S. Small Business Administration's call to provide access to lending and capital that will help create jobs and speed economic recovery.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Citi"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"September 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi commits to lending $24 billion to American small businesses.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Citi"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/citi-commits-to-lending-24-billion-to-american-small-businesses","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"In Marin County, an affluent suburb north of San Francisco, there is an influx of over 60,000 people packing the county's roadways every weekday morning, driving to their jobs from all corners of the nine-county region that makes up the Bay Area. At the same time, approximately 40,000 mostly higher-income Marin County residents leave the area heading for jobs in the city and elsewhere.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Mike Stillman"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"September 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Cutting out commutes to strengthen communities.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Communications Coordinator, EAH Housing"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/cutting-out-commutes-to-strengthen-communities","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Washington, DC - Citi today announced a memorandum of understanding (MOU) with the China General Certification Center (CGC) to advance the development of China's renewable energy sector. ","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi to Coordinate with China General Certification Center (CGC) on Renewable Energy Standards","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-to-coordinate-with-china-general-certification-center-cgc-on-renewable-energy-standards","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"In May, we announced our collaboration with Google, MasterCard, First Data and Sprint on a highly anticipated new technology that brings the power and convenience of credit card payments to your mobile phone. Today, we are proud to help bring the first version of Google Wallet to the public, available initially on Nexus S 4G for Sprint.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Paul Galant"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"September 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Introducing Google Wallet.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["CEO, Citi Global Enterprise Payments"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/introducing-google-wallet","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"If you have children who went off to college this fall, they probably took a lot more items--and a lot more expensive items--than you did when you attended college two or three decades ago. Between the laptop, printer, smartphone, TV and perhaps an expensive bike--as well as clothes and other items--students can easily have several thousand dollars' worth of valuables in their dorm rooms or apartments.","month":"09","author.displayName":["Jonathan Clements"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"September 19, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Renter's insurance for college students.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Director of Financial Education, Citi Personal Wealth Management"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/renters-insurance-for-college-students","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"The international banking corporation Citi today announced plans to establish an R&D (research and development) center in Israel. The group examined various sites in the world and ultimately announced its intention to establish an R&D center for innovation in Israel. The center is expected to officially open during the month of December, but Citi has already begun to recruit new workers from the high-tech sector.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 18, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi to Launch R&D Center in Israel to Support Activity Throughout the World","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-to-launch-rd-center-in-israel-to-support-activity-throughout-the-world","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"San Jose, Costa Rica – The Citi Foundation is sponsoring the XIV Inter-American Microenterprise Forum, FOROMIC, and the Excellence Awards in Costa Rica, which honors microentrepreneurs from the local business community. The seven winners were honored at a breakfast together with the ADRI Association, the MEIC and the Inter-American Development Bank (IDB), FOROMIC's host.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 16, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Honors Top Costa Rican Microentrepreneurs","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2011/citi-honors-top-costa-rican-microentrepreneurs","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Sofia, Bulgaria - Citi Bulgaria provided two new credit lines in the amount of EUR 25 million and EUR 7.7 million to the Bulgarian Development Bank (BDB). The new credit lines are the largest funding Citi has provided to BDB. The facilities will be used for direct investment financing of small and medium enterprises (SME), as well as for trade finance.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 16, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Bulgaria Provides Bulgarian Development Bank with 33 Million Euro Credit Facility","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-bulgaria-provides-bulgarian-development-bank-with-33-million-euro-credit-facility","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"New York – Citibank today announced changes to its banking relationship packages in response to direct feedback from clients on providing clearer choices, more simplicity and greater rewards. Existing customers will begin receiving notification of these changes at the end of this month, with the enhancements becoming effective for all clients in December of this year.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 16, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Simplifies Banking Package Options","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citibank-simplifies-banking-package-options","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup will issue its third quarter results via press release at approximately 8:00 AM (EDT) on Monday, October 17, 2011. At 11:00 AM (EDT), results will be reviewed via live webcast and teleconference. ","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 16, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Third Quarter 2011 Earnings Review","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-third-quarter-2011-earnings-review","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Moscow - Roundtable participants discussed youth-focused policies in the region and examples of programs that involve students in development and implementation of social projects supported or administered by the foundations and NGOs. The participants also summarized the results of a three-year project, \"Involvement of Senior Students in Non-Profit Sector Activity,\" implemented by Focus-Media Foundation via regional NGOs and supported by Citibank.","month":"09","year":"2011","publishDate":"September 16, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","ti