ney while spending money.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 28, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank España Launches \"Todo Cuenta\" (Everything Counts), The First Account That Grows With You","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citibank-españa-launches-todo-cuenta-everything-counts-the-first-account-that-grows-with-you","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Chicago, Ill. – Citi will resume its 2011 <i>Citi Cubs Kids</i> season with back-to-back programs just prior to the Cubs hosting the World Champion San Francisco Giants at Wrigley Field on Wednesday, June 29, and Thursday, June 30. Both programs will be held at The Inter-American Magnet School (851 W. Waveland Ave, Chicago, Ill.), and former Cubs legend Lee Smith and team Chairman and Owner Tom Ricketts will be guest speakers.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 28, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Cubs Kids Program Resumes Its Second Season of Providing Chicago Children Communities with Motivational and Educational Experience","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-cubs-kids-program-resumes-its-second-season-of-providing-chicago-children-communities-with-motivational-and-educational-experience","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"New York – On June 16, Citibank joined <i>The New York Enterprise Report</i> to honor the New York tri-state area's top business advisors at the 2011 Best Accountants and Attorneys for Growing Businesses awards.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 27, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Congratulates Winners of The New York Enterprise Report's \"Best Accountants and Attorneys for Growing Businesses\" Awards","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-relea