le-Click Checkout, a cross-platform, low-friction mobile billing service.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 21, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Ventures Makes Strategic Investment in Mobile Billing Company Billing Revolution","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-ventures-makes-strategic-investment-in-mobile-billing-company-billing-revolution","tags":["Press Release Migration","Citi-Wide"]},{"summary":"Dubai – The Center for Management &amp; Professional Development (CMDP) at University of Dubai and the Citi Foundation recently celebrated the successful conclusion of the joint \"Entrepreneurship and Business Plan Development\" workshop, which trained 19 women entrepreneurs on successful business management skills.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 21, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"U.A.E.: Women Entrepreneurs Successfully Trained on Business Plan Preparation","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/foundation/news/press-release/2011/uae-women-entrepreneurs-successfully-trained-on-business-plan-preparation","tags":["Press Release Migration","Environmental, Social & Governance"]},{"summary":"Prague – Citibank has launched the first contactless Shell MasterCard credit card that allows its holders to make contactless payments at all Shell stations and other retailers equipped with contactless technology. The first successful contactless transactions were made in Žilina in Slovakia and in Jelenia Gora and Wodzislaw Slaski in Poland, where the contactless technology is already widespread and commonly used. Citibank clients, as holders of the first contactless credit cards issued in the Czech Republic, are first to benefit from the contactless technology when making their payments.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 20, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citibank Clients Are the First to