nds with a diverse range of 59 online service providers (and growing), including clubs, schools, universities, internet service providers, utility bill payments, charities and more. Citibank has also introduced the first ever online food order and delivery system in Pakistan as part of its online banking offering.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 10, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citi Pakistan: The Only Bank Powering Payments to More Than 50 Online Partners","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citi-pakistan-the-only-bank-powering-payments-to-more-than-50-online-partners","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Warsaw, Poland – As many as 10,000 clients already enjoy various privileges, discounts and promotions offered by the multi-partner Citibank MasterCard World Credit Card. Developed in cooperation with seven partners, it was launched by the bank at the beginning of 2011. Holders of Citibank MasterCard World Credit Cards may collect points under a multi-brand loyalty program and exchange them for vouchers that can buy products and services from program partners or for <i>moneyback</i> to repay part of their debt. Together with the Citibank MasterCard World Credit Card, clients also get access to discounts, promotions and offerings prepared by Card partners.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 10, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"10,000 Multi-Partner Credit Cards from Citi Handlowy","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/10000-multi-partner-credit-cards-from-citi-handlowy","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"month":"06","author.displayName":["Citi"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"June 10, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"\"The Chiettis Come Clean About Money.\"","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["Citi"],"url":"https:/