nt will be equal to the bill amount, calculated by OAO Mosenergosbyt.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 02, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Russia: Citibank Clients Choose Modern and Accessible Bill Payment Channels","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/russia-citibank-clients-choose-modern-and-accessible-bill-payment-channels","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"Hong Kong/Shanghai - Citigroup and Orient Securities Company Ltd today signed definitive agreements, subject to regulatory approval, establishing a securities joint venture to operate in the Chinese domestic market. The new JV will be called 东方花旗证券有限公司 in Chinese and \"Citi Orient Securities Co. Ltd\" in English.","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 02, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup and Orient Securities Sign China Securities Joint Venture Agreement","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citigroup-and-orient-securities-sign-china-securities-joint-venture-agreement","tags":["Press Release Migration","Institutional Clients Group"]},{"summary":"New York - Citigroup Inc. and Citibank (South Dakota), N.A. today announced the preliminary results as of the Early Tender Date in the previously announced cash tender offers (each, an \"<b>Offer</b>\" and, collectively, the \"<b>Offers</b>\") with respect to the notes listed in the tables below (the \"<b>Notes</b>\").","month":"06","year":"2011","publishDate":"June 02, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Citigroup Inc. and Citibank (South Dakota) Announce the Early Results of Offers to Purchase Outstanding Notes, the Extension of the CCCIT Early Tender Date and an Increased Tender Cap","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/citigroup-inc-and-citibank-south-dakota-announce-the-early-results-o