rk - At an event today, Google, Citi, MasterCard, First Data and Sprint announced and demonstrated Google Wallet, an app that will make your phone your wallet so you can tap, pay and save money and time while you shop. For businesses, Google Wallet is an opportunity to strengthen customer relationships by offering a faster, easier shopping experience with relevant deals, promotions and loyalty rewards.","month":"05","year":"2011","publishDate":"May 26, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Google, Citi, MasterCard, First Data and Sprint Team Up to Make Your Phone Your Wallet","category":"PRESS RELEASE","url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/press-release/2011/google-citi-mastercard-first-data-and-sprint-team-up-to-make-your-phone-your-wallet","tags":["Press Release Migration","Consumer Banking"]},{"summary":"We're pleased to stand today with Google, MasterCard, First Data and Sprint to <a href=\"https://www.citigroup.com/citi/press/2011/110526a.htm\">launch</a> a highly anticipated new technology allowing Citi customers to make seamless purchases with the wave of an Android phone at point-of-sale. It's called the Google Wallet.","month":"05","author.displayName":["Paul Galant"],"year":"2011","publishDate":"May 26, 2011","siteId":"citigpa","type":"insights","title":"Our collaboration on the Google Wallet.","category":"PERSPECTIVES","author.jobTitle":["CEO, Citi Global Enterprise Payments"],"url":"https://www.citigroup.com/global/news/perspective/2011/our-collaboration-on-the-google-wallet","tags":["Perspective Migration"]},{"summary":"Citi was ranked #1 in the Corporate space in Russia in the prestigious <i>Euromoney</i> FX Poll 2011. Results reflect clients' recognition of Citi's leadership, expertise, innovative solutions and superior client service in the category. The survey is a leading review of FX providers and services, and is considered to be the benchmark for the FX industry.","month":"05","year":"2011","publishDate":"May 25, 2011","site